body:
Sarah,

Confirmed. I've reviewed HJ's GeoLocationContext.js and have the fixes ready:

## FIX 1: saveToCloudDefault (line 462-477)

CURRENT:
```javascript
const location = {
  lat: locationData.lat,
  lng: locationData.lng,
  radiusMiles: locationData.zoomRange || 50
};
// ...
body: JSON.stringify(location)
```

FIX:
```javascript
const appId = process.env.NEXT_PUBLIC_APPLICATION_ID || '2';
const location = {
  lat: locationData.lat,
  lng: locationData.lng,
  radiusMiles: locationData.zoomRange || 50,
  appId
};
// ...
body: JSON.stringify(location)
```

## FIX 2: fetchMapCenter (line 536-543)

CURRENT:
```javascript
const response = await fetch(`${azureFunctionsURL}/api/mapcenter`, {
  headers: { 'Authorization': `Bearer ${firebaseToken}` }
});
```

FIX:
```javascript
const appId = process.env.NEXT_PUBLIC_APPLICATION_ID || '2';
const response = await fetch(`${azureFunctionsURL}/api/mapcenter?appId=${appId}`, {
  headers: { 'Authorization': `Bearer ${firebaseToken}` }
});
```

